	PEEK <player/monster>

Peek allows thieves and assassins to try and "peek" at 
another player's or monster's inventory.  If they are 
successful, they get to see what that creature is holding. 
If they are doubly successful, then no one will see that 
the thief or assassin tried to peek.

Mark says, "Hi".
: peek Mark
He is carrying: a bow, a knife.

Related Commands:  steal, stealgold, distract
